data.title: List of Urdu Poets-Wikipedia - 05-01-2014
data.meta_description: List of Urdu Poets-wikipedia- 05-01-2014 - Free download as Word Doc (.doc), PDF File (.pdf), Text File (.txt) or read online for free. This Wikipedia article lists Urdu language poets from the 13th century to contemporary times, arranged by date of birth. It includes over 300 poets across different centuries, from early poets like Amir Khusro in the 13th century to modern poets born in the 1970s. The list provides the name of each poet, their takhallus or pen name, and lifespan. Major poets mentioned include Mirza Ghalib, Allama Iqbal, Faiz Ahmed Faiz, and Parveen Shakir. The article is intended to be expanded further to include additional Urdu poets.
